CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 8, 1954, pg. 11, reads: "Fortieth Anniversary - Snapped by cameraman Teenie Harris is the charming group of guests who attended the Original Junior mothers' Club bridge-luncheon last Saturday at the Ruskin."
TitMainTitle: Group of women wearing hats, seated around tables in interior of the Ruskin for the fortieth anniversary of the Original Junior Mothers' Club bridge - luncheon
